asset.title: Penny Skateboards X Active Ride Shop - Hosoi Signing and Hippie Jump
asset.description:
Penny Skateboards and Active Ride Shop teamed up at the Active Huntington Beach store for a Hosoi signing and Hippie Jump contest during the US Open of Surfing. http://www.pennyskateboards.com

The winner of the Hippie Jump took home a check for $500, and won by jumping just over 58"!

Thanks to Active Ride Shop for teaming up with us and thanks to everyone who came out to the event!
